		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have an idea to add meta sprite editor functionality into NES Screen Tool - one that would allow to align sprites arbitrary with arbitrary palettes. Animation could also be considered. Not sure how it going to look, though, certainly a separate window.

		

