	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One way to achieve this is to not edit the CHR data directly, but instead use some other tool like GraphicsGale, ASEPRITE, etc to do the animation, and then convert the results to CHR using some automated tool (like Tilificator), or manually.<br /><br />That said, a metasprite editor like what Shiru is talking about would certainly be welcome.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


